uiConfig.queryString: 'Log Source' = 'Oracle Fusion Apps: Enterprise Scheduler Service (ESS)' | link 'Request ID' | stats unique(Application) as Application, avg(ElapsedTime) as E, unique('Instance Parent Id') as 'Parent ID', unique('Job Display Name') as Job, unique('Parent Request ID') as 'Parent Req ID', unique('Product Name') as Product, latest('State Description') as Status, unique(Submitter) as Submitter | eval 'Time Taken' = unit(E, ms) | eval U = url('https://oracle.com', View) | eventstats distinctcount('Request ID') as Requests, avg(E) as AE, latest(U) as Details by Product, Job, Status | eval 'Average Time Taken' = unit(AE, ms) | createtable name = 'Job Summary' select Product, Job, Status, Requests, 'Average Time Taken', Details | classify 'Start Time', Job, 'Time Taken', Product, Status as 'ESS Jobs Analysis' | fields -E, -AE
